seo: WebLogic,CVE-2020-14750,远程代码执行漏洞,未授权访问
summary: 该插件用于检测WebLogic服务器是否存在CVE-2020-14750远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断是否存在未授权访问问题。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the WebLogic server has the CVE-2020-14750 RCE vulnerability, and determines if unauthorized access is possible by sending a specific request.
